OL,3,CCouncil overturns climate pledge under
OL,4,Cnew Reform leadership
OL,6,FClimate change commitments set by
OL,7,FWakefield Council have been overturned
OL,8,Fby its new Reform UK leadership.
OL,10,FClimate and biodiversity emergencies
OL,11,Fwere declared in the last seven years
OL,12,Fby Wakefield Council under its former
OL,13,FLabour guise with an aim stated to
OL,14,Fbecome carbon neutral by 2030.
OL,16,FFour years from the target,
OL,17,Fcouncillors have now voted to
OL,18,Fundeclare its climate change and
OL,19,Fbiodiversity declarations.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/5
